{"tid":1676211,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"【行動討論】哀悼受中共政權剝削而偷渡的39名死者","createTime":"2019-10-26T10:01:15.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-27T12:12:58.000Z","uid":132010,"like":29,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"1b9614c05b0a5dcb920cf88826071b96f6426fc9","tid":1676211,"uid":132010,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-26T10:01:15.000Z","msg":"中國低下階層受剝削，經濟不平等，貪污腐敗，先會有咁多人為左揾工作機會而偷渡。大家不如黎一個哀悼死者們嘅集會。<br />\n<br />\n雖然胡錫進係度屌鳩英國唔做野，但人地國家啲難民關注組都出黎係倫敦掉念，BBC頭版都係呢單野，對中國偷渡客關注度好高。<br />\n<br />\n我地要話比世界知，我地關注既係人權，公義。雖然佢地係連登仔最憎既支那人，但佢地都係死於中共下既不平等，受嘅苦難同我地相人似。<br />\n<br />\n加泰集會你地都搞得成，悼念中共政權下既死難者唔會搞唔成掛?<br />\n<br />\n啱聽就幫推！"},{"pid":"59bf3a7b94b597aa9329072e4c156f56ee8b76f0","tid":1676211,"uid":132010,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-26T10:01:43.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ca57433d19eb3ef64fcc76b0c3bd749b2f950c6b","tid":1676211,"uid":132010,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-26T10:01:58.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"63f7a48974e26ebcbeefb9c31487aa7f88582c74","tid":1676211,"uid":74155,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-26T10:03:05.000Z","msg":"聲援聲援過反送中嘅中國義士好過啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ec9112d35a4a81999feb59dc101a7e481c827815","tid":1676211,"uid":165683,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-26T10:03:07.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"5f950cb4e623dcfe6310e8e4e5a5b90ff016b392","tid":1676211,"uid":132010,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-26T10:03:22.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"dffd45d9567d500ff8e7e07b4286e95e3a2a3ea7","tid":1676211,"uid":165683,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-26T10:03:26.000Z","msg":"smart move"},{"pid":"9b5dbdbed1eb8a2d2bd3d599d2f95bb4c42181e8","tid":1676211,"uid":132010,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"dffd45d9567d500ff8e7e07b4286e95e3a2a3ea